p_table <- function(tab_data, ...) {
  tab_data_2 <- deparse(substitute(tab_data))
  
  table_p <- do.call(CreateTableOne, 
                     list(data = as.name(tab_data_2), includeNA = TRUE, ...))
  table_p_out <- print(table_p,
                       showAllLevels = TRUE,
                       printToggle = FALSE)
  kable(table_p_out,
        align = "c")
}
beck_vumc <- read_csv("I:/Brant/Research/Lab Becker/Multi_data/Pain Study Data BeckerENT and VUMC labels 08-30-2017 2.csv",
                       col_types = cols(.default = col_character())) %>%
    rename(ID = `Subject Number`,
           LM_Score = `Lund-MacKay Score`,
           Surg_Date = `Date of surgery`,
           Age = `Age at surgery`,
           Ever_Smoke = `Has participant ever smoked?`,
           Current_Smoke = `Is the participant a current smoker?`,
           Pain_DOS = `Pain Level Day of Surgery`,
           Pain_POD_1 = `Pain Level Post Op Day 1`,
           Pain_POD_2 = `Pain Level Post Op Day 2`,
           Pain_POD_3 = `Pain Level Post Op Day 3`,
           Narc_DOS = `Narcotic  Use - Day of Surgery`,
           Narc_POD_1 = `Narcotic Use - Post Op Day 1`,
           Narc_POD_2 = `Narcotic  Use - Post Op Day 2`,
           Narc_POD_3 = `Narcotic Use - Post Op Day 3`,
           Tyl_DOS = `Tylenol Use - Day of Surgery`,
           Tyl_POD_1 = `Tylenol Use - Post Op Day 1`,
           Tyl_POD_2 = `Tylenol Use - Post Op Day 1_1`,
           Tyl_POD_3 = `Tylenol Use - Post Op Day 1_2`,
           Splints = `Septal Splints?`,
           Packing = `Nasal Packing?`,
           Steroids = `Post Op Oral Prednisone?`,
           DOB = `Date of birth`,
           Date_consent = `Date Consented`,
           Sex = Gender,
           Pt_Complete = `Did Patient Complete the Study?`,
           Reason = `If no, reason`,
           Study_Date = `Date of study completion`) %>%
    mutate(Surg_Date = as.Date(Surg_Date, format = "%m/%d/%Y"),
           DOB = as.Date(DOB, format = "%m/%d/%Y"),
           Date_consent = as.Date(Date_consent, format = "%m/%d/%Y"),
           Study_Date = as.Date(Study_Date, format = "%m/%d/%Y")) %>%
    filter(is.na(Institution) == FALSE) %>%
    select(Institution, ID, LM_Score, Age, Ever_Smoke, Current_Smoke,
           Pain_DOS, Pain_POD_1, Pain_POD_2, Pain_POD_3, Narc_DOS,
           Narc_POD_1, Narc_POD_2, Narc_POD_3, Tyl_DOS, Tyl_POD_1,

data_pain <- data %>%
        select(c(ID_New, Pain_DOS, Pain_POD_1, Pain_POD_2, Pain_POD_3, Current_Smoke_YN, Ever_Smoke_YN,
                 Splints_YN, Packing_YN, Steroids_YN, Sex, Inst_Code, Turb, Sept,
                 FESS, Rhino, DCR, AGE_DEC)) %>%
        gather(Day, Pain, Pain_DOS:Pain_POD_3) %>%
        separate(Day, 
                 into = c("Type","Day"),
                 sep = 5) %>%
        select(-Type) %>%
    unique()
data_pain %>%

        geom_boxplot(color = "grey47") +
